name: THE TICKLE - Issue #18
description:
Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

#17 is the Collectors Issue, featuring personal choices from their collections by legendary H=N advocates Chilltulpa, Cabline & Chris Coleman. Also featuring cover and incidental art by Chris.

Featured writers this week are the poets Prince Magnolia and ST Rivera.

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) and Maia Mellier (@maiamellier)
